08:13.360 --> 08:17.329
when first I come to america,
I know nothing.

08:17.364 --> 08:21.399
How to dress, what to eat.

08:21.435 --> 08:24.703
I sleep in a closet with
a stuck hanger in my jacket

08:24.738 --> 08:28.273
so I don't fall down.

08:28.308 --> 08:30.475
On the street
I hear this phrase.

08:30.511 --> 08:35.413
You know this phrase:
"american values."

08:35.449 --> 08:39.284
and I think,
"what does it mean?"

08:39.319 --> 08:42.521
financial values I understand.

08:42.556 --> 08:46.391
Money. What a thing is worth.

08:46.426 --> 08:49.394
Human values,
this also makes sense.

08:49.429 --> 08:51.396
The things we love.

08:51.431 --> 08:55.400
Family,<i> I bambini...</i>

08:55.435 --> 08:57.702
But this american values:

08:57.738 --> 09:02.707
Land of the free,
home of the brave,

09:02.743 --> 09:05.544
this I don't know.

09:05.579 --> 09:09.247
And then I learn
the history of this country.

09:09.283 --> 09:12.684
Your slavery,
the smallpox in the blankets,

09:12.719 --> 09:15.687
how you stole the land
from the natives.

09:15.722 --> 09:20.325
And I realize...
To be an american

09:20.360 --> 09:22.727
is to pretend.

09:22.763 --> 09:24.629
Capisce?

09:24.665 --> 09:28.733
You pretend to be one thing when
really you are something else.

09:28.769 --> 09:31.436
And I can do that.

09:31.471 --> 09:35.273
Lie. Hide.

09:35.309 --> 09:38.677
But what I will not do
is pretend we are at peace

09:38.712 --> 09:41.580
when really we are at war.

09:44.384 --> 09:46.518
Are we at war?

09:50.691 --> 09:53.558
Not yet...

09:53.594 --> 09:55.760
But we're trying real hard.

09:55.796 --> 09:58.697
It was a step too far, no?

09:58.732 --> 10:00.632
You mean you?

10:00.667 --> 10:03.435
What? No. You steal the guns,

10:03.470 --> 10:06.438
-you kill my man.
-You're shooting
at my boss's boy.

10:08.475 --> 10:09.741
What you say? A shot?

10:09.776 --> 10:11.576
-Who shot?
-Your goons.

10:11.612 --> 10:14.679
Taking a shot
at the boss's boy, the eldest.

10:14.715 --> 10:17.649
Calamita and the rabbi.

10:17.684 --> 10:19.551
And the way I figure,

10:19.586 --> 10:23.455
