we didn't off him, too!

10:32.432 --> 10:34.799
You didn't know?

10:40.641 --> 10:45.810
How about a spring street
stick-up, night before last?

10:45.846 --> 10:47.612
Two dames.

10:47.648 --> 10:50.281
Shotguns, kitchen knives.

10:50.317 --> 10:52.617
Took out two of my boys.

10:52.653 --> 10:55.253
That-that wasn't us.

10:57.524 --> 11:00.492
Well, are you sure?

11:00.527 --> 11:03.628
'cause it seems to me
that you ain't tracked in

11:03.664 --> 11:05.730
