(car door closes)

23:03.449 --> 23:04.548
(car departs)

23:09.272 --> 23:12.206
.
The pump and go out on route 16.

23:12.241 --> 23:14.275
I'm the nightman.

23:14.310 --> 23:18.312
You might tell the marshal
what you told me.

23:18.347 --> 23:20.314
About the lesbians?

23:20.349 --> 23:22.116
Well, there was two of them.

23:22.151 --> 23:25.052
Uh, a injun
and-and a colored woman.

